<Link id="l00598" /><CodeLine lineNumber="598"><Highlight kind="comment">/// Split the specified string over a separator and return a range-compatible</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00599" /><CodeLine lineNumber="599"><Highlight kind="comment">/// iterable over its partitions.  Used to permit conveniently iterating</Highlight></CodeLine>

<Link id="l00605" /><CodeLine lineNumber="605"><Highlight kind="comment">/// \\end</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00606" /><CodeLine lineNumber="606"><Highlight kind="comment">///</Highlight></CodeLine>
